OL,3,CJurors warned of 'publicity' as school
OL,4,Cstabbing retrial begins
OL,6,FThe retrial of a teenage girl accused
OL,7,Fof the attempted murder of two
OL,8,Fteachers and a pupil during a school
OL,9,Fstabbing in Ammanford has got underway
OL,10,Fat Swansea Crown Court.
OL,12,FYsgol Dyffryn Amman teachers Fiona
OL,13,FElias and Liz Hopkins were stabbed
OL,14,Fduring an attack on April 24 2024. A
OL,15,FYear 10 pupil was also stabbed during
OL,16,Fthe incident.
