OL,6,FThe 14-year-old defendant has admitted
OL,7,Fthree counts of wounding with intent
OL,8,Fand a single count of possessing a
OL,9,Fbladed article on school premises,
OL,10,Falthough she denies attempting to
OL,11,Fmurder the victims.
OL,13,FJudge Paul Thomas KC today warned a
OL,14,Fjury that the case had received "a lot
OL,15,Fof publicity" following the
OL,16,Fabandonment of the original trial in
OL,17,FOctober last year.
