OL,6,FJudge Thomas previously said the
OL,7,Foriginal trial had been "irretrievably
OL,8,Fcompromised" before dismissing jurors
OL,9,Fhours before a verdict was expected.
OL,11,FAddressing the new jury he said: "You
OL,12,Fmay have read about it in the press
OL,13,Fand there has already been one trial
OL,14,Fthat had to be abandoned for various
OL,15,Freasons."
OL,17,F"Please put thoughts of all the things
OL,18,Fyou have read in the media out of your
OL,19,Fminds. In particular, avoid the best
OL,20,Fyou can social media which is very
OL,21,Frarely accurate."
