OL,6,FThe jury also heard opening statements
OL,7,Ffrom the prosecution who told them the
OL,8,Fdefendant had said to teacher Ms Elias
OL,9,F"I'm going to f*****g kill you", as
OL,10,Fshe launched an attack with a multi-
OL,11,Ftool fishing knife belonging to her
OL,12,Ffather.
OL,14,FThe court also heard how fellow
OL,15,Fteacher Ms Hopkins was stabbed as she
OL,16,Ftried to restrain the teenage girl
OL,17,Fbefore members of staff intervened and
OL,18,Fsubdued the defendant.
