OL,6,FHowever, the girl then managed to run
OL,7,Fat a pupil and stab them multiple
OL,8,Ftimes before the knife was confiscated.
OL,10,FCCTV of the attack, which happened in
OL,11,Fthe lower schoolyard during a mid-
OL,12,Fmorning break, was played to the court.
OL,14,FThe prosecution told jurors that the
OL,15,Fteenage girl was arrested at the scene
OL,16,Ffor attempted murder and told officers
OL,17,Fas she was being driven away "I'm
OL,18,Fpretty sure this is going to be on the
OL,19,Fnews, so more eyes are going to be
OL,20,Flooking at me, that's one way to be a
OL,21,Fcelebrity."
